00:09:49.700 --> 00:09:51.000
&gt;&gt; Eleanor Billington:
Thank you, Nealy.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:52.300
That was beautiful.

00:09:52.300 --> 00:09:53.600
That's just like the best way
