00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.770
I mean, woo, good weekend.

00:09:55.770 --> 00:09:59.230
Next up is 2016 Poetry Out
Loud Georgia State champion,

00:09:59.230 --> 00:10:00.630
Marta Palombo.

00:10:00.630 --> 00:10:03.070
Marta was the first runner-up
