00:10:03.070 --> 00:10:05.480
She finished in second
place overall.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:09.470 position:56%
She's a recent graduate of Cambridge
High School in Milton, Georgia,

00:10:09.470 --> 00:10:10.940
and just began her freshman year

00:10:10.940 --> 00:10:14.290
