[Laughter] Yes;

00:34:08.580 --> 00:34:09.880
do you recite to your
family, your pets?

00:34:09.880 --> 00:34:11.480
Why don't we start
with Nealy, and yes.

00:34:11.480 --> 00:34:13.280
[Laughs]

