It's like a season for me.

00:36:32.200 --> 00:36:35.400
I lock myself in my room for
about, again, five hours.

00:36:35.400 --> 00:36:37.750
And it's just -- yes, five hours.

00:36:37.750 --> 00:36:39.400
And it's just going over the poem,

00:36:39.400 --> 00:36:40.700
going over the poem,
going over the poem.

00:36:40.700 --> 00:36:42.080
I take it line by line.

00:36:42.080 --> 00:36:44.610
It's kind of also like doing a
