00:36:50.790 --> 00:36:52.090
And then I slow it down.

00:36:52.090 --> 00:36:53.750
And then I say it like
really elaborate.

00:36:53.750 --> 00:36:56.760
So it's like going through it
and just, again, repetition.

00:36:56.760 --> 00:37:00.410
And I definitely agree with Nealy,
the poems that you actually connect

00:37:00.410 --> 00:37:03.340
to are much easier to just like
recite because it's basically

00:37:03.340 --> 00:37:05.020
like telling one of
your own stories.

00:37:05.020 --> 00:37:08.390
But it's five hours of
locking myself in my room.

00:37:08.390 --> 00:37:09.870
[Laughter]

