that's not the right one.

00:42:00.310 --> 00:42:02.680
And then this other guy
isn't so good as well.

00:42:02.680 --> 00:42:05.280
And it's like basically that.

00:42:05.280 --> 00:42:08.760
And it's just like those
moments where I can get onstage

00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:10.800
and tell stories of
what actually happened

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:14.510
to me is what keeps me going,
and keeps me inspired by it.

